<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title>Prelude</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,111,97,0.35), transparent 65%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(201,75,123,0.35), transparent 65%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 10%, rgba(122,95,255,0.25), transparent 70%),
        linear-gradient(160deg, #05070D, #0A0F1F, #1C2541);
      color: #F2C6B4;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-y: auto;
      scrollbar-width: none;
      -ms-overflow-style: none;
    }

    body::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }

    /* Top-left musical arpeggio (fixed) */
    .note-cluster {
      position: fixed;
      top: 1.2rem;
      left: 1.2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: #FF6F61;
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255,111,97,0.7);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    /* Title */
    .title {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: #FF6F61;
      text-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      margin-top: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Content wrapper */
    .content-wrapper {
      max-width: 700px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-bottom: 10rem; /* ensures signature never collides with fixed link */
      position: relative;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: #F2C6B4;
      text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(242,198,180,0.25);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    /* Fixed bottom-left link */
    .home-link {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 1.2rem;
      left: 1.2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #FF6F61;
      padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: rgba(255,111,97,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,111,97,0.45);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,111,97,0.55);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      transition: background 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .home-link:hover {
      background: rgba(255,111,97,0.25);
      box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* Signature inside content flow */
    .signature {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: right;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #F2C6B4;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(242,198,180,0.35);
      transition: color 0.25s ease, text-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .signature:hover {
      color: #FF6F61;
      text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- Musical arpeggio in top-left -->
  <div class="note-cluster">
    <div class="note">♫</div>
    <div class="note">♪</div>
    <div class="note">♫</div>
  </div>

  <div class="title">Prelude</div>

  <div class="content-wrapper">

    <div class="content">
      <p>
        Welcome to all. Instrumental Notes brings together musical instruments from different cultures and traditions. Each one has its own beauty in its sound, in its culture surrounding it, and in its people who convey it through music. This project is a way to appreciate such instruments and to spend time with the character and texture they carry, and I hope you enjoy exploring it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Signature at bottom-right of text -->
    <a class="signature" href="https://github.com/musman-uk" target="_blank">Mohammed Usman</a>

  </div>

  <!-- Fixed bottom-left link -->
  <a class="home-link" href="/">Instrumental Notes</a>

</body>
</html>
